text: Worcester County is a county located in the U.S. state of Massachusetts. As of the 2020 census, the population was 862,111, making it the second-most populous county in Massachusetts while also being the largest in area. The largest city and traditional county seat is the city of Worcester. ==References== Category:Massachusetts counties Category:18th-century establishments in Massachusetts Category:1730s establishments in the Thirteen Colonies Category:1731 establishments
